import React from 'react'; import { useNavigate, useEffect, Link } from 'react-router-dom'; import SendData from './SendData'; import { useAlert } from "react-alert"; export default function ResetPassword (props) { const Navigate = useNavigate(); const [stage, setStage] = React.useState("stage2"); const [username, setUsername] = React.useState(props.username); const [otp_sms, setOtp_sms] = React.useState(""); const alert = useAlert() async function updatepassword(){ let signindata = {data: { Username: username } } let gqlRequest = "mutation SignIn ($data: UsrsigninInput!){ SignIn(input: $data) { Token } }" let response = await SendData(gqlRequest, signindata, 'signin') if ( "errors" in response ){ // if password is a match redirect to profile page //{ProcessErrorAlerts("hi", "hi")} console.log("error resetting", response.errors[0].message ) return false } else {// if password is a match redirect to profile page localStorage.setItem('jwt_token', response.data.SignIn.Token) // Store JWT in storage Navigate ("/Profile/" + username + "/home") } } function alertError(error){ const delimiter = '= ' const start = 2, tokens = error.split(delimiter).slice(start), result = tokens.join(delimiter); // those.that alert.show(result) } return ( <>

Enter the code sent to {props.mobile}
Enter the code sent to {props.email}
Enter your new password
) };
